            <title>[SPARK-4484] [CORE] Treat maxResultSize as unlimited when set to 0; improve error message</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-4484</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
